{"word":"G2433 - ἱλάσκομαι - hiláskomai - hil-as'-kom-ahee - Be merciful","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἱλάσκομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>hiláskomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hil-as'-kom-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be merciful"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கிருபையாயிரு, நிவர்த்திசெய்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to render propitious to oneself, to appease, conciliate to oneself"},{"paragraph":"2. to expiate, make propitiation for"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Middle voice from the same as <a href=\"#/G2436 - ἵλεως - híleōs - hil'-eh-oce/2436\">G2436</a>; to <i>conciliate</i>, that is, (transitively) to <i>atone</i> for (sin), or (intransitively) <i>be propitious:</i> - be merciful, make reconciliation for."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2433 - ἱλάσκομαι - hiláskomai - hil-as'-kom-ahee/2433\">G2433</a>, <a href=\"#/G2434 - ἱλασμός - hilasmós - hil-as-mos'/2434\">G2434</a>, <a href=\"#/G2435 - ἱλαστήριον - hilastḗrion - hil-as-tay'-ree-on/2435\">G2435</a>, <a href=\"#/G2436 - ἵλεως - híleōs - hil'-eh-oce/2436\">G2436</a>"}]}